-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP: -Capstone Mining Corp, Imperial Metals Corp 
-- 
-- Fri Oct 03, 2014 06:53AM EDT
-- None



Oct 3 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Capstone Mining Corp and Imperial Metals Corp, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Capstone Mining Corp <CS.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to buy from hold * Imperial Metals Corp <III.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to speculative buy from hold  Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.* Avigilon Corp <AVO.TO>: Imperial Capital starts with an outperform rating and C$25 target * Canadian Pacific Railway <CP.TO>: CIBC ups target to C$245 from C$240; sector outperformer * Canadian Pacific Railway <CP.TO>: BMO raises target to C$260 from C$240; rating outperform * Canadian Pacific Railway <CP.TO>: RBC ups target to C$205 from C$222;rating sector perform * Capstone Mining Corp <CS.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to buy from hold * Eldorado Gold Corp <ELD.TO>: RBC raises to outperform from sector perform rating * Gabriel Resources <GBU.TO>: RBC cuts target to C$1.50 from C$2.50; rating sector perform * Imperial Metals Corp <III.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to speculative buy from hold * Lake Shore Gold Corp <LSG.TO>: RBC cuts to underperform from sector perform * Lake Shore Gold Corp <LSG.TO>: RBC cuts price target to C$1.15 from C$1.30 * Levon Resources Ltd <LVN.TO>: Europac starts with buy rating * Partners Real Estate Investment Trust <PAR_u.TO>: CIBC raises target to C$4.75 from C$4.50